{"tid":1099831,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"日部落客傳授「一秒A變G杯」超狂祕招","createTime":"2019-04-10T04:44:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T09:10:11.000Z","uid":55981,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"b3f5305abd1ebc334c222172b7915c38df9850f5","tid":1099831,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T04:44:24.000Z","msg":"現在有很多女生為了讓胸部變大嘗試了各種不同的方法，像是狂喝木瓜牛奶、做豐.胸運動、穿集中托高胸.罩、甚至去隆等等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/kho-tin-voi-than-hinh-no-nang-cua-hot-girl-sinh-nam-1996-131642.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fkho-tin-voi-than-hinh-no-nang-cua-hot-girl-sinh-nam-1996-131642.jpg&h=d409e71a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果可以的話，大家都不會想動手術吧。那到底有什麼方法，可以讓A的直接升級到G？<br />\n<br />\n日前有部落客分享了一個靠穿就可以狂升10個罩杯的方法，各位貧乳女子快來看看吧！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/d924238.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fd924238.jpg&h=4f9b9b2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先把絲襪塞進去<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/擷取-25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F%E6%93%B7%E5%8F%96-25.jpg&h=b0010275&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這樣就跟普遍的托高效果一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/擷取-26.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2F%E6%93%B7%E5%8F%96-26.jpg&h=3e8e0596&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/d924228.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fd924228.jpg&h=58e08f6f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n接著再穿上另一個胸罩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/d924231.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fd924231.jpg&h=50d48007&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再穿上另一個&hellip;但記得要調整一下，把副乳全都塞進去！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/d924233.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fd924233.jpg&h=12f1877a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我們先來看看之前的照片&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/d924232.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fd924232.jpg&h=de5b87e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n這是之後！改變實在太驚人了！<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.teepr.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/06/d924230.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.teepr.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F06%2Fd924230.jpg&h=9c7e8099&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"705e3f55ce30b8ee43b87639a30e3fe9b5efa5cc","tid":1099831,"uid":18569,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T04:46:27.000Z","msg":"咁咪好唔撚方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"775b00454af8435389a68f1c3a1da4018035a96d","tid":1099831,"uid":129045,"like":49,"dislike":0,"score":49,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T04:48:04.000Z","msg":"一秒？"},{"pid":"f87d0b235d017942342956fd5752e6f21cdbf110","tid":1099831,"uid":15348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T04:48:39.000Z","msg":"好撚蠱惑"},{"pid":"18af70475b39c24c0e60b8aa17e3b010024042fe","tid":1099831,"uid":196855,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T04:49:32.000Z","msg":"對波會好L硬"},{"pid":"8f3c07fd88a27e48e39523193a222aa1cfec3b52","tid":1099831,"uid":45368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T04:49:35.000Z","msg":"😅"},{"pid":"1ca5e9721f1dd773eac881dd26da99